Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to survive one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,night without being humiliated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My ex would be at the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire elite would be
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,watching, and I couldn't bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to show up alone as the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.85,0:00:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,abandoned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at the altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.52,0:00:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hired an escort, charming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,elegant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He seemed far too dangerous for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,someone paid to smile, but
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,he was the only one who defended
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,me when
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.26,0:00:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they tried to destroy me in
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,public.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.34,0:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is that, in the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,middle of the party, his
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,face appeared on every TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted, dangerous, mafia boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And now the man I hired to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,pretend to be my date might have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,been
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the biggest risk of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed guest list hit my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,phone at 942 in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from the silence the device made
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.67,0:00:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,before it buzzed, that something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.32,0:00:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,was about to ruin my Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a robe, barefoot in the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,apartment kitchen,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,balancing a black coffee in my
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,right hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and my work tablet in my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The hotel's charity gala was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.06,0:01:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,happening that night, and I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,spent the entire week pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it was just another event.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretending was the most constant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,exercise of my adult life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd perfected it after the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened the file. I scrolled my
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,finger down the names in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,alphabetical order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The coffee went cold in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,before I reached the letter H.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.82,0:01:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin H. plus one. I set the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,cup down slowly, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,delicacy of someone defusing a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and sat on the counter because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,my legs had decided this was a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,good moment to stop cooperating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I said to myself out loud to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the refrigerator, which had no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.23,0:01:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.40,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. The plus one next to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,his name bothered me more than
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the name itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew who the plus one was. The
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.95,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,whole city knew. Tisha Rome had
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,posted three times the previous
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,weekend, a video of herself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,trying on dresses, saying, in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the voice of someone chewing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,meringue,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,that she was going to the gala
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,of the year, with an old love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,turned new.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Old love turned new was the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,elegant way of saying, Noelia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,crosses exfiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.88,0:02:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleguance never fooled anyone in
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicago. I stood up. sat down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,stood up again. Walk to the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,window and back. The first
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,crisis was about the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd chosen a black one. Long
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,modest neckline, entire back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,exposed, because I wanted to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as the woman who organized the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,gala, not as the woman who
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,showed up to be stared at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the dress seemed like a
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,joke. Too modest. Too sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Address for someone who'd given
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The second crisis was about
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin's parents. They'd be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there. Their hotel was three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,blocks
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.54,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from mine. They'd been signing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.15,0:02:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,checks to the charity foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,since before I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And his father had the sinister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,habit of calling me dear. As if
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the word still had a one-way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,ticket to our future. The third
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,crisis, the worst, came when I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,sat back down on the counter and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,realized that Chicago had far
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,too good a memory for a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd been left at the altar and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,remained single. The city didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,forget. The sponsors didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,forget. The society columnist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.04,0:03:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,forget. And I, no matter how
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,many years I'd spent bearing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that night under spreadsheets,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't forget either. The
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,doorbell rang. I know you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I said before I could even
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,open the door. I know you. I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the list. I brought decent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because yours is poison. Sir, I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dom had been my best friend and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,catering partner for six
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,years. And she had the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,peculiarity of treating handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,men like poorly packaged
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,problems and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,emotional crises like recipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She walked in on low heels, hair
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,pinned up on top of her head,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,two paper cups in her hand, and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,a bag hanging from her shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that smelled like butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin confirmed. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,closing the door behind her. I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,read it. With tisha, I saw her
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,video with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the mustard colored dress. Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I set the cups on the counter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and looked at me. You look like
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,slept three hours. I slept four.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lire. She nudged me onto a stool
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and set the cup in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I sniffed it. It was coffee with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,cinnamon and something sweet I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,could never identify.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The ritual. Higher an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, I said, without preamble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,biting into a croissant that had
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared out of nowhere in her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,hand. I choked, what? You heard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,me? Sir, I know, Elia. I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.95,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,going
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to hire a man to pretend he's in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,love with me. You don't need him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to pretend he's in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You just need him to pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,he's present. She chued. The
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,difference is the budget. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You're going to walk into
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that hall alone. With Calvin and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,his influence are laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at the front table and the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsors looking at you like
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.95,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,they're watching a documentary
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,about a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,wounded animal. Is that what you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,want? Sir, I know. Fourth time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll cave. I looked at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked back at me. Calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chewing. With the patience of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who'd already won the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,argument
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,before it started. I sighed. I
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,took a long sip of the cinnamon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee. I looked at the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the tablet. I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,at the name Calvin, hearth plus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,one on the screen and felt that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,heightness in my chest. The
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,tightness that always came when
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about having to smile
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for photographers while he
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.52,0:05:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,walked by. How do you even hire
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an escort on a Saturday? Surai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of smile I should have
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,learned to distrust. She pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,her phone from her back pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,pushed it toward me. App,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,discreet. Elite only. Triple
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,verification. Contractual
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,confidentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already open on the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,registration page. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,terrifying. I'm efficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the phone. The screen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,showed a dark, sober interface.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No photos of shirtless men. No
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,clingy promises. Just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,registration fields. A suggested
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hourly rate. And a clause in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,small letters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,saying the escort offered no
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,service beyond social
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,companionship. I read it twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I breathed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I filled in the field sitting on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the kitchen counter while Surai
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,watched me with the attention of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,an observing surgery. Name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia Cross. Event. Charity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gala. Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Black tie attire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Duration. Five hours. Notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Needs to know how to behave
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,among sponsors. Needs to not ask
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,questions. Needs to be handsome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to shut the mouth of a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,man named Calvin hearth. I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,deleted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the last line. Re-rooted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.46,0:06:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute discretion. Impeccable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,presentation. I tapped confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The app charged my card without
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,ceremony. A confirmation message
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,appeared saying a compatible
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,profile would be assigned within
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,two hours and that the escort
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,would arrive at the provided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,address
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at seven o'clock sharp. Done. I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,said. And my stomach dropped a
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,whole inch inward. Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Surai repeated satisfied. I just
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,made the dumbest decision of my
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,life. You've been making
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.92,0:06:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,dumb decisions since I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a constant. I only support
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the ones with address involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed despite myself. The
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh came out half horse. Half
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Half terrified. Surai pushed me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the bathroom with the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,rest of the croissant in her
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.12,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And the order to shower while
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,there was still time. I arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hotel at five in the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I came in through the back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,service door. As always, because
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to see the operation from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,inside before heading up to the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,hall. The main lobby was already
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,being set up. Tall arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of white hydrangeas, gold ropes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the red carpet I'd argued about
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with the general manager for
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,three
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks. I crossed the interior
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway to the event room on the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,second floor. And the smell of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,wax
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and citrus perfume reminded me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that this was my ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of Calvin, of Tisha,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of hired men or messages from my
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,mother asking if I decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,cut my hair. The team was
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,information. Flores checking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,volume. Meatree'd reviewing the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,dinner sequence. Sound engineer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,testing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,microphone. I passed by each
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,one, repeating the day's orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,adjusting a table cloth here,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,moving a stand there, pretending
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,with reasonable success that my
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,heart wasn't beating an extra
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,count per second. It was when I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,came up the side hallway of the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.43,0:08:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,lobby that I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin was standing near the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,reception desk, chatting with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the evening receptionist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,with the rehearsed smile of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who knows he's being
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,watched. Hair combed to the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,side,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,navy suit, champagne colored
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,tie. He saw me before I could
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,turn toward the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia, he said my name the same
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,way he always did, drawing out
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the final vowel,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the name were still a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,caress. Calvin, what a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,coincidence. You're at the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,event.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a coincidence. It's a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,list. He smiled, walked three
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,steps toward me, slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with that calm of a man who
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,loves having an audience, and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,stopped five feet from me. He
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,smelled
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,like the same bitter cologne
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from two years ago. The smell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,gave me a small wave of nausea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pit of my stomach. You
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,look beautiful. He said, low,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you always look beautiful when
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you're
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nervous. I'm not nervous. You
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,are. You bite the inside of your
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cheek. You still do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped biting the inside of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my cheek. I hated that he was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,right. Calvin, I have an event
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You always had events to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,run. He leaned in slightly, just
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.44,0:09:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the shoulder, just enough that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.34,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,one could hear but me. Tish is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,excited to meet you. I told her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd understand. You always
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The blood went cold somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,between my collarbones and my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,chin. I smiled. It was a trained
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,professional. The kind I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,reserved for difficult clients
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and curious journalists. How
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,sweet. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and my voice came out firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which I silently thanked some
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,goddess of sarcasm for. Tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,were a second, just one. His
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,smile wavered. He recovered
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could savor it. You
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.86,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't changed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a bit. Neither of you. I turned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,my back before he could find his
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,next line. I climbed the side
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with the calm of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't fleeing. On the first
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,landing, I pressed my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and waited for the blood to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,return to my fingers. The wall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,was cold. So were my fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,phone buzzed in my pocket. I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,took it out. I looked. The
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,message from the app glowed on
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the screen with a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.44,0:10:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,neutral notice. Your escort for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the evening will arrive at the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel's main entrance in 15
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Confidentiality confirmed. Enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the event. I breathed. I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.59,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,at the hallway clock. There were
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly 15 minutes until a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,stranger would come through the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel's revolving door and take
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd bought. For some reason, in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that instant, with my hand still
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed against the cold wall
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and my heart still out of rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,because of Calvin. I had the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.87,0:10:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,very clear sensation that I was
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to make a mistake. In a way I
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't yet learned to name. The
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel's backstage had a smell of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,its
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,own. Wax, reheated coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,perfume from the flower shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The faint tang of the tile, the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,cleaning
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,crew scrubbed before every big
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,event. I got there five minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.43,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,early, pretending to check the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,positioning of the waiters. When
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.65,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,really I was just looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,something to do with my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't smoothing my dress for
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the 20th time. The service
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,entrance door opened behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.85,0:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,click of the lock. The soft
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,brush of rubber against the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,waxed floor and I didn't turn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,around immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a professional habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Never show haste. Miss Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The voice came low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Controlled. Without the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,inflection of a real question,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it was a confirmation disguised
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I turned around. He was standing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,three steps away. Both hands
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,loose at his sides. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,first
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,thing I noticed was that he
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't looked for my face first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes had passed before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the service door behind my
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,head. The fire exit to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The hallway that descended
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,toward the kitchen on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Only afterward did they land on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,me. It took a second. Maybe too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I noticed. Yes, I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Evren, that was all. No last
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,name. No handshake. None of that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,pasturized smile I expected from
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,someone paid to smile. He was in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,his early 30s, maybe 35.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.86,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Tall enough that I had to lift
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,my chin. Broad shoulders beneath
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a black tuxedo that looked like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it had been tailored to the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,exact shape of his body. Dark
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,hair. Combed back without
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,rigidity. His
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,beard freshly shaved in a few
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,hours ago. I could see the clean
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,line along his jaw from where I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,stood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The cologne. I noticed because I
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,noticed everything. Was woody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Discreate. The kind that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't announce anyone's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,entrance into any room. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the cologne of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,announce. Noelia. I said because
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it was my turn. Thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,coming on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't short notice. What do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you mean? The request came in at
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,11. It's 7 o'clock. That's 8
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell if he was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,correcting me or just making an
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,observation. His face gave
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I breathed. Do you have
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the briefing? I do. Any
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,questions? No. You don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,know who the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know who the X is. I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,blinked. How? You wrote in the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,notes field that the escort
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,needed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to be handsome enough to shut
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the mouth of a man named Calvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He tilted his head slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin hearth. I presume. There
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't many Calvin's on this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,city's list of charity sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I deleted that line. I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered deleting it. I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,deleted that note. The app
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,archives drafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He gave a half smile that lasted
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a sixth of a second. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,enough for me. Some small alarm
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,fell lit up somewhere behind my
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,collarbone. I ignored it because
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I had 30 minutes to get into the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,hall and no intention of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,starting a negotiation with a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,man I'd already paid. Let's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,agree on something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, you smile when you need
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to. You touch my arm when we
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,pass near the head table.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't give your last name to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone because I won't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,to explain it. If anyone asks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how we met, it was through a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,mutual friend at a dinner last
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,month. And we prefer not to give
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,details because it's recent. Are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,we clear? He looked at me in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,silence for a whole breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A complete breath. Slow. His
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,chest moving once beneath the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,tuxedo. Yes. Anything else? One
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't have to pay me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to touch your arm. I didn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what to say to that. He kept
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at me with the same
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,irritating calm of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.65,0:14:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,had never. At any moment, had to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,make an
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,effort to be heard in a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The cold backstage light caught
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the side of his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,marking the angle of his jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And for a second, I understood
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,why the entire hall would stop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to look
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the moment he walked in. I
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the clock above the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,door to escape my own thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was 7-10.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. I said, we went up the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,side stairs to the main entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of the hall. I walked in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt at some point between the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,second and third flight of
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs that he was watching me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had the impression that he
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.39,0:14:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,watched like someone studying a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,map. Not like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,appreciating
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of you. The difference gave me a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,slight chill at the nape of my
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,neck that I made no move to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,shake off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When I pushed open the double
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,doors of the hall, the murmur of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,voices greeted me like a wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chandeliers, silver, white
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,hydrangeas, roughly 200 people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,in formal attire arranged among
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,round tables, waiters
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,circulating with glasses of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,champagne. The smell was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,different here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut flowers, open wine,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,expensive perfume mixing in the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.47,0:15:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,air conditioning. I walked in
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He came in a step behind me and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his hand rose, unhurried, until
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it settled on the small of my
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a possessive touch. It
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,was a precise touch. As if he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated the angle, the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pressure,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the exact spot where his palm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,would fit without sliding and
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,without gripping. My breath
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,forgot to beat. I hated my own
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,body for it. The hall noticed. I
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Three heads turned first, then
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,five, then the entire hearth
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,table. The silence lasted two
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,whole seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The kind of silence that falls
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,when a room needs to decide what
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,it's seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the murmur returned. Lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with questions. Where two? Ever
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an asked, close to my ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sponsors table. To the right. We
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,walked. He kept his hand on the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,small of my back for the first
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,five
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,meters and then slid it to my
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,elbow, with the same precision
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of someone who improvises no
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I greeted the pharaoh couple
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.49,0:16:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with a smile, exchanged two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.87,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,words with Mrs. Leeman about the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,foundation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and went on introducing my
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,escort with the calm expression
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of someone who did this every
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever an, I would say. Ever an,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he would repeat. Low, shaking
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hands with economical firmness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No one asked for a last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because the way he said
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,his first name closed the door
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin intercepted us near the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,third table. I saw him stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,before he reached us. Tisha was
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,beside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In a mustard colored dress
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly like the video. Smiling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with the caution of someone who
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,yet decided which side of the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,story she wanted to be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Noelia, Calvin said, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,extended his hand to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Everan. Calvin hearth. We
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't met. Everan looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the extended hand. It took half
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He shook it. Everan, just
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everan? For now. Calvin laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the answer were a joke. It
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't know Elya tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin said, turning to Tisha
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with that detestable plural of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,his.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some old history here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She and I almost got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tisha smiled only with the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,corner of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,her mouth. It was the smile of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,someone hearing that line for
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the fifth time that day. Almost
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't count.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, it does count. Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,replied, we know how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we? Always a little
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned to Everan. Good luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,brother. It was at that instant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that Everan moved. Not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,step, half a foot forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough for his shoulder to cover
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,part of my line of sight to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin. His
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.78,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,hand returned to the small of my
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,back with deliberate calm. His
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,voice came low, unaltered, and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,settled in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the air like a knife set on the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,table with no intention of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:17:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,wounding, but with the blade
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,perfectly on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. hearth, Everan paused, just
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,a fraction. The hotel campaign
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,of 2022 had an interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,deficit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine you've already
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,clarified the matter with the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsors present here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps this isn't the moment to
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,offer anyone good luck. The hall
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't hear. It was a two-line
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,remark,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,set at the volume of table
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation, without the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.85,0:18:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,atrics. But I saw the color
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,drain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,glass with a force that whitened
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,his knuckles. I saw Tisha lift
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,her eyes from the table for the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,first
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,time all night, and look at
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Everan with a new and very
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,attentive curiosity. Excuse us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin said,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and his voice came atone above
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,normal. Tisha needs to touch up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,her makeup. I don't. Tisha said
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,quietly, you do. He pulled her
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,by the elbow. They left toward
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the side hallway. I stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Everan's hand stayed on the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,small of my back for another
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,three seconds, and then slid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:18:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,away with
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,same calm with which it had
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived. I turned my face to
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,look at him. His chin was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,lowered, watching the spot where
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin had left, with the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.31,0:19:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,cataloging.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that? I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,whispered. He looked at me. Miss
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross. How do you know about the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,2022
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,campaign? I read. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,published. I read what wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,published. The answer fell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,between us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exact weight of a door
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,being closed. I opened my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to insist. Before I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a man approached from the right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,side. Tall, thin, black suit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,without a tie, and closed around
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,glass of water, and stopped half
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,a step from Everan with the
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,discrete deference of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,who wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there to take part in any
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,conversation. Sir, the man said,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,low, the car is where you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dario. Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.08,0:19:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for now. Dario looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a brief look,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,professional. The kind that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,registers height, posture,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,position of the hands. He
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,inclined his head of
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,fraction in my direction as a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,greeting. Miss, hi. Good
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,evening. He stepped three paces
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,back
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,without turning his back on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Everan, and stood at the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,distance of a newspaper reader
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,in a dentist's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting room. I looked from
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario to Everan, from Everan to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario, back to Everan's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hanging
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,loose at his side. To the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,tailored tuxedo. To the way the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,entire hall kept turning toward
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,him every
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,15 seconds without knowing it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was doing it. Everan, I said, my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,voice lower than I intended.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.80,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,do hired a scorts have their own
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,drivers? He looked at me for a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,whole breath. He didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The corner of his mouth rose a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,millimeter, and the millimeter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,bothered me more than any
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence would
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,have. He extended his arm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,slowly, and set his hand on my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,elbow with the exact precision
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,before, and led me toward the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,head table without answering. I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,went. I smiled at Miss's
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lehman for the second time. I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.04,0:20:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,accepted a glass of champagne a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,waiter offered me. I took a
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,sip too small to lower the level
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the glass, and while I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,smiled, with the hand of a man I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,had bought resting on my elbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,as if the elbow were already
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,his. I felt at some exact point
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,between my ribs. A cold
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,certainty settling slowly, layer
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,by layer, like water cooling in
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't hired an escort. I had
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hired something else. And that's
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,something new,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in a way that still wouldn't let
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.86,0:21:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,me breathe properly. Exactly who
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.60,0:21:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin Harth was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly where the exits of my
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.69,0:21:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,hall were, and exactly how to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,touch my body without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.20,0:21:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner began the way all nights
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,begin when something is about to
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.30,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,break,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with silverware clinking too
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,loudly, rehearsed voices and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter lasting five seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,longer than
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,needed to. I was seated at the
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,head table between the vice
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,president of the foundation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the wife of the main
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsor, feeling everyone's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,resting on the back of my chair
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.04,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,touching me. It was worse than
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,if he'd been touching me. With
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.65,0:21:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,every breath, I remembered he
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.40,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:21:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,attentive, watching, choosing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.18,0:22:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the timing of his own words,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,like someone choosing when to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin was three tables ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.20,0:22:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,beside Tisha. He was laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with his head tilted to the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he always did when he
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted people to think he was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,charmed. Tisha on the other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,had stopped laughing since
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern's remark about the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,campaign deficit. She was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,listening now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,really listening, chin propped
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.31,0:22:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,on her hand, and her eyes met
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.04,0:22:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,mine twice in less than five
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked up the water glass. My
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.56,0:22:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth was dry in a way wine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.12,0:22:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't fix. You've eaten three
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,bites. Evern observed, low,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,without turning his face toward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,me. I counted. Are you counting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,my
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,bites now? I've been counting
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,everything since I walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The sentence went down my spine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,like a
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,shiver. I tried to smile at the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.63,0:22:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsor's wife, who was
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.78,0:22:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,commenting on something about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the table
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,decorations. And answered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.24,0:22:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically that it had been
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the team's idea. It was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.98,0:22:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,had been mine. I'd spent three
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,weeks choosing those white
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,hydrangers because they matched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:22:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the tone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:22:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of the linen napkins, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't remember that properly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,right now. The folder was in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel. The first time I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.47,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,dismissed it. The second, I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,dismissed it again. But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,with Calvin laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,three tables ahead and the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.06,0:23:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsor's exchanging looks about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.78,0:23:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the complicated history, he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,whispered
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes before dinner began. The
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,folder stopped being an option,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.28,0:23:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and became the only thing I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,could see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.60,0:23:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I set the napkin beside my
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.08,0:23:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,plate. I need to take care of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,something quick backstage. I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,said to the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,table, with the rehears smile of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who's worked at a luxury
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel for nine years. I'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for dessert. Ever looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said nothing. He just made a
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,minimal movement with his chin,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a nod that wasn't a nod, but
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.61,0:23:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,which I interpreted as go. I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.59,0:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,keep watch. I left through the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.50,0:23:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.76,0:23:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway. The lights there were
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,lower than in the hall, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.12,0:23:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,carpet absorbed the sound of my
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.83,0:23:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,heels.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.66,0:23:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I crossed the discreet little
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,door that led to the events
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:23:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,office, and opened the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.93,0:23:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,drawer of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,my desk. The folder was where
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd left it. Brown, unlabeled,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath the box of old business
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the folder with both
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,hands. The paper scraped against
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the metal of the drawer,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sound made me close my
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes for a second. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.62,0:24:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in months that I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.08,0:24:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,touched it,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,without thinking it was a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,mistake. I came back down the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway with the folder pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,against my
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,chest. I passed a waiter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.72,0:24:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying a tray of empty
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.22,0:24:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,glasses, and he nodded to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not noticing what I was
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,carrying. Good. The fewer people
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.54,0:24:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who noticed, the better. I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.23,0:24:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,entered the hall through the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.05,0:24:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,side door
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.64,0:24:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and went straight to the main
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.23,0:24:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsor's table without passing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.93,0:24:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,my chair. Calvin saw me before I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.68,0:24:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,reached it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.52,0:24:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,His smile wavered. Noelia. He
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,said, already on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.35,0:24:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Already with that tone of
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.09,0:24:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,someone about to
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.20,0:24:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,make a joke to minimize
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.41,0:24:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,someone's presence. We were just
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.10,0:24:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,talking about. I know what you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.69,0:24:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,were talking
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.32,0:24:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,about. I interrupted. I set the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.25,0:24:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,folder on the table between the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.17,0:24:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,two bottles of wine. And I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,brought
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.22,0:24:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,context. Three sponsors looked
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.13,0:24:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at the folder. The fourth, a
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.91,0:25:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,white-haired man named Rubin
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.69,0:25:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O'Tiano.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.64,0:25:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at my face. He was the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.04,0:25:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,only one at the table with real
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.55,0:25:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,authority over the foundation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And he'd known me since I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,started at the hotel. What
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.99,0:25:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,context? Rubin asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.86,0:25:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened the folder. Documents,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.88,0:25:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,statements, copies of receipt
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,side obtained through internal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.72,0:25:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,channels because at the time, I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,still thought I was just keeping
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.23,0:25:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,them for myself. For the day I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.90,0:25:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,might need to prove to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.75,0:25:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that he had done what he'd done.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.79,0:25:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2022, the hands that welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.76,0:25:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,campaign raised $318 ,000. I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.88,0:25:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,said, my voice firmer than I
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.01,0:25:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,expected. 142
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.46,0:25:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,,000 were
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.40,0:25:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,diverted before they reached the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.91,0:25:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,receiving foundation. The
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.09,0:25:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,transfer receipts came from the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.56,0:25:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,corporate
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.98,0:25:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,account that had shared
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.22,0:25:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,authorization from the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.40,0:25:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,campaign's then-guest financial
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,director.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.10,0:25:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin Harth, the silence at the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.12,0:25:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,table was immediate. Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.83,0:25:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed. The laugh came out
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.54,0:25:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,choked.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.98,0:25:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is absurd. He said, Nolia,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.34,0:25:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you have personal
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.63,0:26:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,grievances but using a charity
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.92,0:26:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,campaign too. It's not a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.41,0:26:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,grievance, Calvin. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.83,0:26:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,accounting. Rubin took the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.44,0:26:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,papers without asking
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.74,0:26:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,permission. He leafed through
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.40,0:26:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,them in silence. The pages made
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.18,0:26:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that dry sound of something
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.73,0:26:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,being
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.02,0:26:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,read carefully. The other
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.67,0:26:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsor, a woman named Helena,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.64,0:26:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,stretched her neck to look along
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.75,0:26:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.34,0:26:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept my eyes on Calvin. There
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.51,0:26:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is also a voice said behind my
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.61,0:26:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder, a second account.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.08,0:26:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Opened in the Caribbean in the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.51,0:26:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,name of a shell company called
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.94,0:26:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Harthwell Consulting. It
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.08,0:26:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,received
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.46,0:26:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,three deposits from the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.94,0:26:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,corporate account and amounts
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.80,0:26:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that add up almost exactly to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the campaign's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.56,0:26:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,deficit. I didn't have to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.64,0:26:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to know. Everin had come. Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.86,0:26:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,swallowed drily. His color
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.66,0:26:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,turned
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.08,0:26:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,strange. Tisha, behind him, had
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.27,0:26:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,stood up from her chair and had
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.46,0:26:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,her purse in her hands. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.37,0:26:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,fleeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.56,0:26:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet. But positioning her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.26,0:26:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,body so no one would confuse her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.21,0:26:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,with him. How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin asked. His voice came out
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.21,0:26:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in octave higher. Everin took
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.89,0:27:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,half a step to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.72,0:27:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt his shoulder brush mind
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.49,0:27:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,lightly. I know many things. He
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.31,0:27:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.46,0:27:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Some because it's my job. Others
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.01,0:27:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're written in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.28,0:27:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,places that men like you forget
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.78,0:27:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,exist. Rubin closed the folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.52,0:27:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at Calvin with the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.10,0:27:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of someone who had
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.73,0:27:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,already
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.12,0:27:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,decided. Calvin, I'm going to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.99,0:27:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ask you to leave our table.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.73,0:27:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin opened his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.56,0:27:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Closed it. Saw Tisha with his
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.55,0:27:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes. Tisha looked away. He
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.40,0:27:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to laugh one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.39,0:27:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The last
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.94,0:27:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,resort of cornered men. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.91,0:27:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,laugh died before it became
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.63,0:27:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,sound. He stood up. Grabbed his
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.60,0:27:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,blazer
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.98,0:27:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,from the back of the chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.66,0:27:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tisha didn't go after him. She
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.53,0:27:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,sat back down. Perse still in
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.34,0:27:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,her lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.84,0:27:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And cross her legs like someone
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,who decided to watch the rest of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.86,0:27:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the night from a better angle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.84,0:27:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I stood still for three seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.39,0:27:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,after Calvin left the field of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.89,0:27:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,view. My heart was beating so
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.34,0:27:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,hard
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.54,0:27:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it in my jaw. Rubin
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.85,0:27:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,reached his hand across the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.22,0:27:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,table and touched my hand for a
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.79,0:27:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.64,0:27:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A brief paternal gesture. From
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.19,0:27:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the generation that still
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,believed a touch could replace
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.03,0:27:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.24,0:28:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Noelia. I nodded. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.50,0:28:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,trusting my voice. Everin
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.27,0:28:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,touched my back. Light. Almost
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.39,0:28:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.96,0:28:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just enough to remind me I was
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.09,0:28:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,still standing. I turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.36,0:28:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Air. I said. It was the only
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.34,0:28:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,word that fit in my mouth. This
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.11,0:28:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,way. He guided me through the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.77,0:28:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,hall without haste, without
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.32,0:28:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,drawing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.72,0:28:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,attention. Weaving between the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.53,0:28:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,tables as if we were just taking
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.45,0:28:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a normal stroll. We passed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.02,0:28:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sarine near the side door. She
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.95,0:28:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,had appeared who knows when and
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.95,0:28:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,her eyes were wide with pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.89,0:28:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.08,0:28:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,gave a thumbs up. I nearly
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,laughed. I couldn't. The side
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.82,0:28:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,door led to the service hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.00,0:28:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.20,0:28:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,same one I'd cross to get the
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.67,0:28:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,folder. The lights there were
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.14,0:28:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,still low. The sound of the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.76,0:28:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,grew muffled when the door
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.10,0:28:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,closed behind us. I pressed my
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.64,0:28:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,forehead against the cold stone
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.23,0:28:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,wall for
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.64,0:28:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,a second. I let out my breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.71,0:28:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everin stayed three steps back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.85,0:28:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting. I never thought I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.78,0:28:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,managed to do that. I said
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,without turning around. I'd kept
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.57,0:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,those papers for months. I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.40,0:28:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,decided
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.86,0:28:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to die with them in
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.64,0:29:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the drawer. What changed? I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.18,0:29:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,thought about it. It wasn't the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.96,0:29:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,folder.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.36,0:29:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't Rubin. It wasn't even
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.31,0:29:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin trying to laugh. You knew
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.32,0:29:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the name of the bank in the
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.02,0:29:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Caribbean. Silence. I turned
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.91,0:29:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,around. He had his hands at his
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.00,0:29:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,sides. The matte black jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.95,0:29:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,absorbing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.56,0:29:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the little light in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.47,0:29:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me without
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.84,0:29:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,answering right away. I did. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.68,0:29:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,admitted.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.90,0:29:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow. Because I came here tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.57,0:29:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,for something else, noelia. And
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.24,0:29:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin's name was on the list of
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.96,0:29:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,other things. I felt my stomach
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.96,0:29:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,dropped two floors. It wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.84,0:29:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly fear. It was something
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.78,0:29:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.36,0:29:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensation of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.49,0:29:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,realizing that the floor they'd
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,been standing on was a ceiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.00,0:29:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and that there was an entire
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.80,0:29:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,room underneath. I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.67,0:29:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,who you are. You don't. He
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.35,0:29:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.40,0:29:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I should ask you now. You
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.03,0:29:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,should. He didn't move. Neither
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.06,0:29:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,did I. The hallway was quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.89,0:29:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.74,0:29:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear my own breathing and
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.46,0:29:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,his, both out of rhythm. Why
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.19,0:29:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't you tell me you knew? I
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.03,0:29:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.86,0:29:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I was going to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.83,0:29:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, simply. I was going to
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.80,0:30:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,let you believe it was just luck
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.84,0:30:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that I knew about Calvin. And I
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.38,0:30:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was going to let the night
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.67,0:30:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,follow the path I'd planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.50,0:30:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was going to leave before
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.34,0:30:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee. That was the plan. And
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.10,0:30:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a step. Not two. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.07,0:30:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,three. One step calculated. In
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.19,0:30:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that way of his of calculating
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.30,0:30:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.64,0:30:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The distance between us became
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.98,0:30:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,small in a way that changed the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.36,0:30:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,temperature of the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.96,0:30:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened was you going to
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.79,0:30:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,get the folder alone. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.62,0:30:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened was you returning
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.44,0:30:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to the hall without asking for
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.20,0:30:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,my help, without asking for
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.79,0:30:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.50,0:30:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened was me realizing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.08,0:30:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,in the middle of dinner that it
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.72,0:30:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,was the first time in a long
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.20,0:30:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,while
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that I wanted to know someone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.25,0:30:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and not decode them. I looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.23,0:30:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,him. Really looked. Without
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.90,0:30:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pretence,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.00,0:30:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without the professional filter
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.58,0:30:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the events manager, without
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.11,0:30:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the wall I'd built since the
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.53,0:30:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,altar.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.30,0:30:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He came closer. His hand rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.32,0:30:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly, giving me time to pull
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.34,0:30:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,back if I wanted. And his
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.03,0:30:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.50,0:30:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,brushed the side of my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.11,0:30:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stopping just before my chin. It
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.96,0:31:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was the lightest gesture anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.75,0:31:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.92,0:31:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,made toward me in years. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.79,0:31:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the most dangerous gesture. I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.67,0:31:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,not going to kiss you. He
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.18,0:31:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,murmured.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.30,0:31:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want me to, I
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.95,0:31:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted him to. Wanted it so much
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.99,0:31:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it frightened me. His mouth was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.96,0:31:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.02,0:31:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,centimeter from mine. I felt the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.75,0:31:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,heat of his breath hit the
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.15,0:31:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,corner of my lips. His finger
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.72,0:31:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.04,0:31:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,still on my jaw. Without
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,pressing. Without deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.68,0:31:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,anything for me. I closed my
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.72,0:31:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes. I tilted my
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.96,0:31:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,face half a millimeter. I pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.93,0:31:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,back. Not because I didn't want
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.85,0:31:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Because I wanted it in a way
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.82,0:31:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have permission to want
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.67,0:31:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,yet. You pulled back the same
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.34,0:31:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,measure. Without sign, without
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.07,0:31:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,complaining,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.44,0:31:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,without demanding. You just
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.15,0:31:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled back. His hand dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.98,0:31:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and returned to his side. It's
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.88,0:31:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,okay. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.20,0:31:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was okay. In a
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.51,0:31:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,frightening way it was. I was
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.32,0:31:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,going to say something. I don't
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.26,0:31:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.88,0:31:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe thank you. Maybe wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.60,0:31:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When the halls internal intercom
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.57,0:31:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,crackled through the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.92,0:31:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My assistant's voice shrill,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.92,0:32:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,called my name. Miss Cross,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.86,0:32:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,urgent, main hall. The screen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.93,0:32:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,programming
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.72,0:32:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,changed and we couldn't identify
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.50,0:32:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of the signal. I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.00,0:32:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at Evern. He was already
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.73,0:32:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,looking
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.12,0:32:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,at me. And for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.05,0:32:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,all night, I saw something
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.78,0:32:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,crosses face, something very
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.64,0:32:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.52,0:32:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,very controlled, that he crushed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.48,0:32:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could name it. I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.01,0:32:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,crossed the service hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.66,0:32:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,almost running, with Evern a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.42,0:32:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,step behind me. My heels struck
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.37,0:32:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the concrete floor and the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.38,0:32:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,echoed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.76,0:32:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,off the low ceiling. Mixed with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.45,0:32:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the smell of grease and
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.70,0:32:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,industrial detergent that had
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.28,0:32:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,impregnated that hallway for
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.09,0:32:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,years. And I thought, in a
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.77,0:32:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,disconnected way, that I'd never
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.83,0:32:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,run in
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.22,0:32:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that hallway in nine years at
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.07,0:32:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the hotel. In nine years I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,always had time. The screen
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.58,0:32:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,programming
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.28,0:32:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,was something I controlled with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.94,0:32:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,a click on the central panel. It
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.65,0:32:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't change on its own. It had
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.36,0:32:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,never changed on its own. I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.95,0:32:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,pushed the side door with my
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.60,0:32:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder. I returned to the
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.19,0:32:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.96,0:32:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing I noticed was
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.91,0:32:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the silence. 500 people dressed
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.99,0:32:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,in formal attire, frozen with
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.94,0:33:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,glasses in hand looking up. The
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.91,0:33:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of silence that isn't an
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.74,0:33:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,absence of sound. It's wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.04,0:33:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when everyone holds their
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.54,0:33:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,breath at the same time and the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.10,0:33:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,air in the room changes quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.28,0:33:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The four screens of the hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.01,0:33:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,two on the side walls, two above
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.93,0:33:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the stage, were all displaying
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.72,0:33:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the same image. A federal
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.57,0:33:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,bulletin, the red banner
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.35,0:33:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,underneath red, official notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.72,0:33:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.84,0:33:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and above the banner, filling
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.72,0:33:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the entire frame, was ever in
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.61,0:33:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Melvani's face. It was a file
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.49,0:33:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.46,0:33:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,black and white, of him in a
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.02,0:33:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,dark jacket, looking at the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.53,0:33:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,camera with the same calm he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,me within the service hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.56,0:33:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes before. Beneath the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.30,0:33:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,name, in smaller letters, it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.10,0:33:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,read,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.42,0:33:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,head of the Melvani family,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.34,0:33:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted for criminal association,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.62,0:33:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,money laundering, conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.52,0:33:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I stopped breathing. The
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.67,0:33:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,narrator's voice kept talking
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.05,0:33:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in my brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.54,0:33:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but I couldn't process the
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.10,0:33:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,words. I could process only one
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.96,0:33:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thing. His hand had been on my
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.76,0:33:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That same hand, two minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.24,0:34:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,before. Someone started
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.70,0:34:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,whispering to my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.70,0:34:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Another person to my right. The
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.42,0:34:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,sound grew like a wave. It began
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.19,0:34:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,at the back of the hall and
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.68,0:34:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,came toward me, and in five
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds the 500 people were all
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.21,0:34:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,talking at once. I saw heads
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.91,0:34:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,turn toward
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.58,0:34:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,me. I saw hands covering mouths.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.91,0:34:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw Rubino Tiano at the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.74,0:34:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsors table. Look at the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.71,0:34:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,screen,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.74,0:34:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then at me with an
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.04,0:34:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,expression I couldn't decipher.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.88,0:34:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't judgment, but it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.41,0:34:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't neutrality
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.42,0:34:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,either. It was the look of
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.14,0:34:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,someone still deciding what to
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.12,0:34:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,think. Calvin smiled. I saw him
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.17,0:34:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly near
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.96,0:34:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the main door. He'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.82,0:34:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he'd come back, and he
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.80,0:34:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,had the blazer still over his
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.59,0:34:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.26,0:34:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And he smiled for the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.29,0:34:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,all night. It was a small,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.93,0:34:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,contained smile. The kind he
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.70,0:34:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,saved
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.02,0:34:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for victories he hadn't expected
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.63,0:34:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to receive. I knew him well
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,enough to know the specific
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.36,0:34:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.76,0:34:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he was feeling at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.35,0:34:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure of watching the
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.83,0:34:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,narrative turn against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.54,0:34:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,without him having to do
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.10,0:34:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. Ever entouched my
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.86,0:35:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,elbow. Softly, just two fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.94,0:35:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he knew exactly how much
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.66,0:35:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,pressure was enough to move me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.38,0:35:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without startling me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.82,0:35:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to the corner. He murmured. Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.96,0:35:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I went. Not because he ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.96,0:35:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it. Because the hall was turning
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.10,0:35:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,into something I didn't know how
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.10,0:35:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to control, and the corner near
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.04,0:35:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the Westwall was the only place
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.98,0:35:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,where I wouldn't be watched by
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.45,0:35:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone at once. I pressed my
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.91,0:35:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder against the column.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.76,0:35:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The stone was cold through the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.48,0:35:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,fabric of my dress, and I stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.31,0:35:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there for a second, just
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.68,0:35:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.20,0:35:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,before I looked at him. I hired
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.57,0:35:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you. I said, my voice so low he
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.94,0:35:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,had to lean into here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.00,0:35:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For three photos. To shut Calvin
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.18,0:35:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,up, to leave before coffee. I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,know. I didn't hire you to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.26,0:35:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,headline
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.80,0:35:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on national television ever. I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.88,0:35:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,know. I know is not an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't raise his voice. He
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.98,0:35:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.40,0:35:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,try to justify himself. He just
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.24,0:35:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me. With that calm I
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.02,0:35:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,now understood wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.26,0:35:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.18,0:35:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,difference with subtle, but it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.67,0:36:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was there. It was in the way his
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.25,0:36:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes swept the room while they
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.74,0:36:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,looked
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.04,0:36:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,at me. Always both processes at
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.42,0:36:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,once. I owe you an entire
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.34,0:36:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,explanation. He said, I'll give
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.72,0:36:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,it to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.10,0:36:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you, but not now. Why not now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.31,0:36:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they came for me. I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.30,0:36:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't understand immediately. I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.65,0:36:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,spent
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.02,0:36:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,a few seconds looking at him,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.91,0:36:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,processing. Hearing the hall's
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.87,0:36:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,murmur grow again, as the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.50,0:36:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsors
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.02,0:36:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,raised their phones in the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.40,0:36:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,waiter's stop-tap way. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.93,0:36:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,only when the murmur began to
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.47,0:36:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,turn
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.68,0:36:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,to movement. People grabbing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.53,0:36:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,purses. People looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.25,0:36:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,exits. That I heard the first
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.16,0:36:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,shout come
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.82,0:36:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from the service entrance. Not
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.63,0:36:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,from the main entrance. From the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.57,0:36:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,service entrance. The entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.38,0:36:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself had shown the team that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.26,0:36:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon. The entrance in the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.02,0:36:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,side hallway that the sponsors
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.78,0:36:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,families never saw. It took the
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.70,0:36:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,time of seeing three men enter
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.55,0:36:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,through the side hallway. In
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.28,0:36:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,black coats. In dark gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.00,0:36:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,With short guns they weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.72,0:36:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,pointing at anyone yet. But
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.37,0:36:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,which
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.68,0:36:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,were on display clearly enough
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.16,0:36:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that no one had any doubt about
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.70,0:36:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,what they were. The hall
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.89,0:37:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,understood
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.38,0:37:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,before I understood. There was a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.29,0:37:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,collective movement. 500 people
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.15,0:37:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to move away from the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.82,0:37:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,service entrance at the same
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.40,0:37:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,time. Glasses fell. And the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.92,0:37:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sound of crystal hitting the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.50,0:37:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,marble floor
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.18,0:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,cut through the air. A woman
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.92,0:37:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,screamed. The three men didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.79,0:37:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,shoot. They just advanced two
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.59,0:37:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,steps
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.90,0:37:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,into the hall and stood still.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.37,0:37:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spreading fear the way you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.65,0:37:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,spread the front page of a
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.93,0:37:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.06,0:37:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,calmly. Taking their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.90,0:37:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody leaves. The one in the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.95,0:37:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,middle said. His voice was low.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.70,0:37:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Trained. The kind of voice you
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.38,0:37:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,learn in silence. Nobody takes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.05,0:37:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out a phone. We want one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get them, we leave. I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at Evern. Evern looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.00,0:37:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the three. The three looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.78,0:37:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.30,0:37:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The calculation happened in his
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.94,0:37:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes in less than a second. I
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.48,0:37:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,saw it. I saw him measure the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,distance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.44,0:37:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to the back door. I saw him
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.00,0:37:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,measure the distance to the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.57,0:37:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,alternate service exit. I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.24,0:37:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,him measure
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.88,0:37:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario, who had appeared who
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.73,0:37:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,knows when. Leaning against the
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.85,0:37:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,opposite wall. As if he'd always
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.04,0:37:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,been there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.72,0:37:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and who had his right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.50,0:38:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden under his jacket. Evern
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.54,0:38:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,could leave. He had roots. He
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.53,0:38:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,had time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.50,0:38:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He had Dario. He didn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.35,0:38:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He turned his face toward me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.13,0:38:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes found me with a
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.61,0:38:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,precision
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.16,0:38:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that made me freeze. As if he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.14,0:38:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,calculated exactly where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.05,0:38:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,before even looking. And I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.97,0:38:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.16,0:38:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,precision form there. In a place
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.99,0:38:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,between the jaw and the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.70,0:38:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mouth. A decision he
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.24,0:38:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't verbalize. But which I
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.77,0:38:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,read is if it were written in
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,large letters on the wall behind
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.99,0:38:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.34,0:38:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was going to stay. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.37,0:38:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,insane. I whispered. Maybe. He
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,answered. Without looking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.32,0:38:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,They came for you. You leave
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.79,0:38:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,through the back now. They'll go
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.47,0:38:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,after you. And the hall gets to
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.10,0:38:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,breathe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.24,0:38:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And what if one of them shoots
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.63,0:38:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,before he sees me leave? 500
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.87,0:38:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,people. You. Surai. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.16,0:38:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The word came down like a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.43,0:38:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Final. The kind of no that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.57,0:38:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,has no argument left after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at the hall. I looked
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.54,0:38:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,at the sponsors cornered near
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.11,0:38:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the tables. At the waiters
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.51,0:38:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,paralyzed
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.00,0:38:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with trays in their hands. At
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.68,0:39:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tisha, who'd crouched behind a
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.42,0:39:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,chair and was looking at me with
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.27,0:39:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,wide
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.50,0:39:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes. Her hand pressed against
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.48,0:39:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,her own chest. I looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.19,0:39:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin. Calvin, who had tried to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.30,0:39:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,escape
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.70,0:39:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,through the main door and was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.15,0:39:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,being held back with surprising
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.69,0:39:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,force. By his own girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,who was whispering something
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.86,0:39:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,furious in his ear and wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.76,0:39:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,let him move. I registered the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.59,0:39:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,scene
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.90,0:39:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for less than a second. But it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.56,0:39:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was enough for something small
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.21,0:39:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and involuntary to break loose
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.87,0:39:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.74,0:39:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you need me to do? I
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.48,0:39:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,said, everyone looked at me. For
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.46,0:39:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time all night. For
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.26,0:39:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the first
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.82,0:39:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,time since he'd walked into the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.70,0:39:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,backstage hours before. I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.46,0:39:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,his expression crack. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.16,0:39:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.98,0:39:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was almost imperceptible. It
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.86,0:39:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was the time of one breath. But
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.75,0:39:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it. You don't need to do
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.57,0:39:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.12,0:39:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, you're not going to
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.32,0:39:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,solve this alone. Not in my
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.45,0:39:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel. No whileia. I know every
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,exit
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.20,0:39:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in this building. I know the
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.76,0:39:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,security control panel. I know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.44,0:39:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how to shut off access floor by
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.17,0:39:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.94,0:39:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to tell me what you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.58,0:40:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,need or I'm going to start doing
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.23,0:40:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it my way and you're going to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.72,0:40:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,be left behind. He looked at me
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.59,0:40:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for another second. The hall
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.27,0:40:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,continued in the background. The
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.20,0:40:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,murmur of the guests. The low
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.83,0:40:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,voice of one of the armed men
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.46,0:40:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,giving an order I didn't quite
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.14,0:40:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.42,0:40:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But between me and Evern, there
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.27,0:40:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,was a bubble of a different
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.88,0:40:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,silence. I saw something cross
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.66,0:40:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.70,0:40:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,something like shock, something
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.40,0:40:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,like respect, something like a
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.05,0:40:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,third thing I didn't have the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.65,0:40:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,vocabulary
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.20,0:40:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to name and decided not to try
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.21,0:40:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to name in that moment. All
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.03,0:40:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,right, he said, you're way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.34,0:40:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario appeared at our side
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.85,0:40:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,without making a sound. I hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.71,0:40:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,even seen him move, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.34,0:40:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,detail alone
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.04,0:40:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,was enough to remind me who I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.86,0:40:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,was dealing with. Sir, Dario,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.69,0:40:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,she's going to the control room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.70,0:40:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You go with her. Through the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.46,0:40:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,back of the pantry, Dario asked
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.40,0:40:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,without altering his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.58,0:40:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the back of the pantry,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.18,0:40:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I confirmed. The service stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.78,0:40:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,lead straight to the monitoring
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,room
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.58,0:40:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,on the mezzanine. Dario made
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.19,0:40:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,half an expression I interpreted
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.02,0:40:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,as approval. He looked at Evern.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.40,0:41:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And you? I stay here. They want
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.41,0:41:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to see me. I'll let them see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.49,0:41:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The right way at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.00,0:41:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone, alone in front, not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.33,0:41:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,behind. Dario nodded. He touched
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.66,0:41:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.90,0:41:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A brief, firm gesture of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.10,0:41:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd known another man for a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.23,0:41:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,long time, and didn't need words
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.58,0:41:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to say what he was saying. Then
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.65,0:41:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,he turned to me. Miss Cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.52,0:41:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. I looked at Evern
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.32,0:41:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,one last time before leaving. He
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.24,0:41:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,was standing leaned against the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.10,0:41:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,column. Hands in his jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.72,0:41:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,pockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.76,0:41:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With the posture of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.09,0:41:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting for the waiter to serve
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.61,0:41:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the second course. The jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.03,0:41:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.18,0:41:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Matt Black, and there was
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.53,0:41:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing in the position of his
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.15,0:41:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulders. In the tilt of his
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.71,0:41:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,head.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.98,0:41:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In the rhythm of his breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.60,0:41:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that gave away what he was about
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.33,0:41:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to do. No one looking at him
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.84,0:41:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there. In that moment. Would
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.34,0:41:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,have guessed that he'd just
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.79,0:41:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,decided to hand his own body
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.29,0:41:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,over to
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.66,0:41:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,three armed men to buy time for
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.84,0:41:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,me. I wanted to say something. I
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.09,0:41:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't. I turned. I followed
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.06,0:41:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario through the side door. The
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.85,0:41:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,same one from the service
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.25,0:41:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway. The same one from the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,almost kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.06,0:42:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The same one I would never again
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.48,0:42:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to cross without
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.55,0:42:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,remembering the centimeter that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.93,0:42:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.20,0:42:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,happen. We crossed the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.79,0:42:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway. The smell of grease
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.45,0:42:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,back. The orange emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.98,0:42:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,lights on the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.78,0:42:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The pantry was empty. The
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.21,0:42:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,waiters all paralyzed in the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.80,0:42:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,hall. The silver trays still
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.40,0:42:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,holding
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.80,0:42:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,sparkling wine warming inside
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.34,0:42:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the glasses. Dario opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.89,0:42:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,back door of the pantry without
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.53,0:42:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.78,0:42:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As if he'd already studied the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.34,0:42:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,floor plan before entering the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.90,0:42:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel. The staircase was narrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.06,0:42:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,metal, with a handrail of tubing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.23,0:42:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,painted black. How many floors?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.33,0:42:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked. Already climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.16,0:42:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Two. The monitoring room is on
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.22,0:42:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the mezzanine. Who's there right
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.42,0:42:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.00,0:42:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcello. From the night crew. I
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.01,0:42:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,trust him. Trust him enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.90,0:42:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,leave Mr. Melvani in his hands
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.78,0:42:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.16,0:42:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have to. Trust him enough that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.82,0:42:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,he won't get in the way. Dario
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,made half an expression again.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was beginning to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.16,0:42:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,that this was his expression for
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.89,0:42:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,acceptable. And that it was the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.56,0:42:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,most
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.78,0:42:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,approval I was going to get that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.59,0:42:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,night. We climbed the stairs in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.35,0:43:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,silence. My heels struck the
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.94,0:43:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,metal
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.22,0:43:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sound rose along with me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.22,0:43:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought briefly about
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,taking them off. Decided not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.14,0:43:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That I would need to move fast
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.75,0:43:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually. And that running
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.25,0:43:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,barefoot on an industrial floor
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.92,0:43:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.08,0:43:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,worse than running in heels. We
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.94,0:43:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,reached the mezzanine. The
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.50,0:43:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway up there was narrower,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.30,0:43:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with faded
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.90,0:43:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,carpet and a row of light
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.34,0:43:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,fixtures that flickered
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.67,0:43:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,slightly. I crossed to the door
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.45,0:43:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of the monitoring room.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.08,0:43:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I knocked three times. The
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.82,0:43:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,internal code the night crew
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.68,0:43:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,used. Marcello opened. His eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.75,0:43:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,were wide and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.62,0:43:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was a cup of coffee in his hand
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.46,0:43:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd forgotten to set down. Miss
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.36,0:43:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross. The hall. I know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.73,0:43:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcello.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.68,0:43:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me in. He stepped aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.46,0:43:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario came in behind me and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.18,0:43:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,closed the door. The room was
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.02,0:43:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,small.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.80,0:43:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An entire wall of monitors
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.54,0:43:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,showing every hallway, every
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.42,0:43:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,exit, every floor of the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.50,0:43:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.70,0:43:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,consoles with keyboards worn
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.12,0:43:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from so much use. Three office
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.64,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,chairs that had never been
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.96,0:43:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.96,0:43:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It smelled a old coffee and
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.35,0:43:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,plastic heated by the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.01,0:43:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I went straight to the main
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:43:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,console without taking my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.99,0:44:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,off the monitors. My fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.48,0:44:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,knew the way from having entered
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.18,0:44:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that room so many times during
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.16,0:44:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,events. I'm going to isolate the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.28,0:44:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,hall. I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,more to myself than to the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.08,0:44:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,others. Access blocked floor by
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.97,0:44:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,floor. The police come in only
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.79,0:44:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,through
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.22,0:44:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the back of the kitchen, which
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.74,0:44:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only route they're not
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.21,0:44:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,covering. Have you called the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.68,0:44:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,police?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.62,0:44:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario asked. Marcello called the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.36,0:44:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,instant the men came in through
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.04,0:44:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.96,0:44:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you Marcello? I did miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.17,0:44:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it on the camera's the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.10,0:44:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,same second and I called.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.38,0:44:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Estimated a rival time. Five
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.23,0:44:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes. That was two minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.14,0:44:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ago. Three minutes. I looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.18,0:44:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.38,0:44:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hall monitor. Everyone was still
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.42,0:44:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,standing. Leigned against the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.27,0:44:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,column. Motionless. With the
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.06,0:44:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,impossible calm of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.67,0:44:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,expecting no danger. The three
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.53,0:44:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,armed men were advancing slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.45,0:44:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.88,0:44:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the middle of the tables,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.30,0:44:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,sweeping the hall with their
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.90,0:44:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes, pushing the guests toward
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.67,0:44:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the walls
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.18,0:44:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with the simple presence of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.16,0:44:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,their bodies. I swallowed drily.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.51,0:44:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario. Miss. How many minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.64,0:45:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,can he hold on his own? Dario
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.41,0:45:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at the monitor. Looked at
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.37,0:45:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,me. His expression didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.90,0:45:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,change a millimeter and that was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.54,0:45:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the most honest answer I could
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.08,0:45:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,have received. Depends on what
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.62,0:45:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,you managed to do up here. I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.38,0:45:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,placed both hands on the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.88,0:45:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,console. My fingers trembled. I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.83,0:45:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,felt
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.08,0:45:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,them tremble against the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.71,0:45:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,plastic of the keyboard. I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.18,0:45:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,forced them to stop. I breathed
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.93,0:45:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,through
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.32,0:45:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,my nose. There was no time to
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.24,0:45:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,tremble. There were five
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.83,0:45:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes. Three armed men. Five
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.82,0:45:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.28,0:45:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,guests. A man leaned against a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.98,0:45:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,column in the hall who had
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.46,0:45:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,decided to stay for me and a
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.05,0:45:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,keyboard
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.50,0:45:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath my hands. I started
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.17,0:45:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,typing. The console in the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.77,0:45:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,mezzanine monitoring room had 14
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.75,0:45:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,buttons
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.18,0:45:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,in three screens and I knew each
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.04,0:45:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,one of them like I knew my own
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.79,0:45:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,handwriting. Marcello stood
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.36,0:45:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,behind me. Your piece in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.83,0:45:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeating in a low voice the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.47,0:45:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,instructions the police were
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.11,0:45:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,giving
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.46,0:45:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,over the radio. Seven minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.53,0:45:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what we had before they
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.75,0:45:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,arrived. Dario closed the door
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.82,0:45:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.96,0:45:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the room and stayed inside. Back
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.65,0:45:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall. Watching the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.24,0:45:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway through the frosted
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.66,0:45:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.44,0:46:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The room smelled of hot plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.16,0:46:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and old coffee. Marcello's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.60,0:46:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,coffee, which he must have
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.04,0:46:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.54,0:46:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in the machine hours before and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.61,0:46:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,no one had thrown out. Start
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.48,0:46:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,with the third floor. Dario
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.29,0:46:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.02,0:46:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,isolate from top to bottom. Push
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.89,0:46:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,them into a single point. I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.46,0:46:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed the first button. The
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.15,0:46:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.62,0:46:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lights on the third floor
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.96,0:46:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,flashed red on the central
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.35,0:46:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,screen. I cut off access to the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.01,0:46:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,internal
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.44,0:46:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs on the right panel. It
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.95,0:46:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,was strange how my hands weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.61,0:46:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,trembling. I'd been trembling
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.12,0:46:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,since the screen lit up his
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.98,0:46:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,face. And now, with a gun on the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.18,0:46:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,floor below and an impossible
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.17,0:46:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,decision
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.72,0:46:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in my throat, I was steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.75,0:46:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that was how you crossed
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.00,0:46:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,through fear. By working.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.00,0:46:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whereas he, I asked, without
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.01,0:46:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,taking my eyes off the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.17,0:46:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dario didn't have to ask who I
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.33,0:46:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,was talking
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.88,0:46:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,about. Ground floor. Behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.08,0:46:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,bar. Alone? He preferred it that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.38,0:46:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,way. I pressed the next button
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.02,0:46:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,harder than I needed to. The
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.86,0:47:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,second floor dropped on the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.64,0:47:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,sensors. The hall. On the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.75,0:47:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.14,0:47:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Was now isolated from the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.64,0:47:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,service hallways. Exactly where
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.50,0:47:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the three intruders had come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.82,0:47:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcello, talk to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.34,0:47:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to come in through the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.01,0:47:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,loading ramp. Not the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.98,0:47:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The front is only clean and
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.24,0:47:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,appearance. There are civilians
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.68,0:47:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed against the lobby wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.62,0:47:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the ramp they come out
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.12,0:47:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,right behind the bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.18,0:47:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.30,0:47:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am. I had never been ma'am to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.09,0:47:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcello. He'd called me no
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.59,0:47:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,alias since the hotel's opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.92,0:47:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With that familiarity of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.29,0:47:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,who's gotten through the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.62,0:47:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,many events together
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.48,0:47:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without needing protocol. I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.03,0:47:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at Dario. He had that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.64,0:47:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,expression that was no longer
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.30,0:47:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.30,0:47:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And not yet worried. It was pure
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.24,0:47:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,attention. The attention of
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.88,0:47:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,someone trained not to waste
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.57,0:47:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.68,0:47:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to ask me if I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.71,0:47:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,know what I'm doing? I said, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.04,0:47:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not? Because he chose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.50,0:47:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He answered. And he doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.00,0:47:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,choose wrong. I swallowed the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.60,0:47:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,reply before it came out of my
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.27,0:47:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.84,0:47:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't the time to discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.37,0:47:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,what that sentence meant. Nor
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.90,0:48:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,how much it unsettled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.22,0:48:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The third screen lit up with the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.82,0:48:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,image from the whole camera. The
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.41,0:48:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,guests were settled against
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.76,0:48:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the east wall. Hands visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.43,0:48:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Some sitting on the floor. Some
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.21,0:48:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,leaning against the edges of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.06,0:48:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.06,0:48:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tisha held Calvin's arm as if he
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.87,0:48:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,were a child trying to escape a
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.63,0:48:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,vaccine. The three armed men
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.22,0:48:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and black coats and dark gloves
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.14,0:48:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,were positioned in a triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.00,0:48:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One at the main door, one at the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.98,0:48:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,side door,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.90,0:48:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,one circling the bar. Behind the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.94,0:48:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,bar, in a blind angle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.73,0:48:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.18,0:48:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ever in with standing. I knew he
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.94,0:48:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was because I saw the eyes of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.53,0:48:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the intruder circling the bar
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.12,0:48:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.34,0:48:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for half a second in the same
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.09,0:48:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,direction on each pass. He was
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.89,0:48:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,being watched and he knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.84,0:48:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And he didn't move. He's
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.50,0:48:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,waiting. Dario murmured. Waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.72,0:48:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.78,0:48:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to finish. I raised my
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.77,0:48:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes to him. How long until I
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.70,0:48:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,finish? Two minutes. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.49,0:48:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.16,0:48:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back to the panel. I cut
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.17,0:48:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,off the fourth floor. The fifth,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.24,0:48:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the penthouse. I cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.80,0:48:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,access to the service elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.56,0:48:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if one of them tried to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.33,0:48:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,flee upward carrying someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.52,0:49:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted it to stop halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.83,0:49:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,through the trip. I locked the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.29,0:49:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,door to the old vaults
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.35,0:49:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.46,0:49:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I locked the event room. I
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.71,0:49:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,locked the office where Calvin's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.24,0:49:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,folder had slept for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.10,0:49:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Each button was a closed door.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.79,0:49:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was strange how I hadn't
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.32,0:49:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,realized. Before that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.24,0:49:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,how many doors the hotel had.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.73,0:49:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How many I controlled without
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.21,0:49:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,ever thinking of it as power.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.70,0:49:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Done. I said, Dario nodded once.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.96,0:49:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come down with me to the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.15,0:49:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,mezzanine hallway. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.52,0:49:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,then you stay. I go down to the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.91,0:49:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,ground floor. I'm coming with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.14,0:49:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you. No. Dario. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.08,0:49:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The open the door. We went out
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.73,0:49:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,into the hallway. The emergency
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.43,0:49:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,lights had come on in a few
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.91,0:49:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.70,0:49:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Giving that place the appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.26,0:49:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of a ship that had decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.66,0:49:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sink with class. The
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.64,0:49:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,moss-colored
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.22,0:49:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,carpet muffled the sound of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.65,0:49:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps. And that absence of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.25,0:49:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sound made everything heavier.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.84,0:49:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,More concentrated. We went down
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.00,0:49:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the internal stairs. Two
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.68,0:49:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,flights. On the landing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.28,0:49:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,between the second floor and the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.96,0:49:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,ground floor, Dario stopped me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.53,0:49:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with his palm held up in the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.00,0:49:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,air. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.02,0:50:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, here is where you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.11,0:50:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You listen. If the police come
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.07,0:50:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,in before I get out,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.58,0:50:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you open the stairwell door for
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.34,0:50:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,them and disappear down the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.88,0:50:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sweet hallway. A greed? A greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.14,0:50:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You went down one more flight
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.46,0:50:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and disappeared around the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.54,0:50:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,curve. I stayed there. Pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.94,0:50:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,against the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.82,0:50:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,light that my hands trembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.48,0:50:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from fear of what might
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.02,0:50:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,happen to me. From fear of what
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.79,0:50:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,might
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.08,0:50:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,happen to him. It wasn't two
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.90,0:50:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes. It was six. I know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.66,0:50:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because I counted by the hallway
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.75,0:50:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.58,0:50:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which sat above a service door
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.19,0:50:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never noticed before that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.74,0:50:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,night. A cheap lock with a white
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.46,0:50:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.22,0:50:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,completely out of keeping with
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.63,0:50:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the hotel's standard, which must
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.13,0:50:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,have been left there by some
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.44,0:50:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,employee
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.82,0:50:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on the palm. Over night shift
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.40,0:50:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who needed to know the time
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.87,0:50:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,without opening his phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.28,0:50:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At the fourth minute, I heard a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.36,0:50:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,dull thud on the floor below. A
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.45,0:50:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,body on the ground. Two quick
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.40,0:50:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.34,0:50:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence. At the fifth, I heard a
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.82,0:50:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,voice I recognized. Not Dario's,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.29,0:50:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,not Evern's. A third lower,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.88,0:51:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,saying a word that sounded like
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.49,0:51:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,an order in another language.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.99,0:51:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound came muffled,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.68,0:51:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it were coming from inside
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.36,0:51:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a wall. And I wondered if I was
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.98,0:51:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,hearing it or imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.74,0:51:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At the sixth, the service
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.16,0:51:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway door beside where I was
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.91,0:51:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,opened. It wasn't a police
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.39,0:51:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.28,0:51:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of the intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.23,0:51:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Black mask, short gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.76,0:51:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,breathless. His left shoulder
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.79,0:51:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,darkening around a
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.04,0:51:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,wound he hadn't yet noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.38,0:51:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,would bleed twice as much as it
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.91,0:51:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,already was. He'd come up the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.35,0:51:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.60,0:51:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,stairs. The stairs I'd thought
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.27,0:51:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,were locked and weren't because
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.99,0:51:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd forgotten that specific
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.49,0:51:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,access.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.40,0:51:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The access of the fire exit that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.83,0:51:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,connected the ground floor
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.99,0:51:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,directly to the mezzanine
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.11,0:51:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,without passing
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.78,0:51:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,through the elevator. He saw me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.56,0:51:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,before I could react. His eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.27,0:51:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,were normal. That was the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.71,0:51:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,frightening part.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.68,0:51:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ordinary eyes of someone who was
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.77,0:51:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,afraid, bleeding, and wanting to
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.85,0:51:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,get out of that place alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.14,0:51:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He raised the gun in my
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.70,0:51:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,direction. Where? He said, out
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.72,0:51:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of breath. Where's the exit? I
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.75,0:51:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.26,0:51:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it was courage
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.94,0:51:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,or if it was the surprise that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.61,0:52:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,froze everything. I stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.07,0:52:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.46,0:52:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,against the wall and opened for
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.24,0:52:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,him to see. And the only thing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.97,0:52:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that came into my head was
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.46,0:52:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,surized line from the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.28,0:52:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the night about poorly
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.75,0:52:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,packaged problems. Sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.39,0:52:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,what looked
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like decoration was danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.61,0:52:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes what looked like
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.12,0:52:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,danger just wanted a door. He
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.80,0:52:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,took a step
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.44,0:52:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,toward me. I asked, he didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.22,0:52:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,finish. Ever and appeared around
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.19,0:52:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the curve of the stairs behind
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.04,0:52:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,him
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.22,0:52:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with a speed I couldn't describe
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.03,0:52:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,afterward. There was no shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.67,0:52:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a short technical
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.19,0:52:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,movement,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.24,0:52:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,almost bored. The kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.81,0:52:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,precision that comes from years,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.82,0:52:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,not from rage. And the intruder
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.76,0:52:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,was on
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.14,0:52:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the ground. With the gun three
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.97,0:52:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,meters away, his wrist twisted
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.79,0:52:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,at an angle no one recovered
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.50,0:52:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.74,0:52:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that surgery. And his head
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.00,0:52:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,hanging to the side after the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.41,0:52:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,sharp blow ever and had
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.52,0:52:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,delivered to the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.30,0:52:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,base of the neck. Ever and
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.85,0:52:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me. His tuxedo was
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.53,0:52:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,still intact, except for the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.20,0:52:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,left sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.40,0:52:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where a dark line of blood had
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.15,0:52:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,drawn a diagonal stroke. It
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.73,0:52:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't his. I knew it wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.37,0:52:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,his,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.76,0:52:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because he was standing the same
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.28,0:52:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,way as before. But that
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.37,0:52:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,particular stillness of someone
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.84,0:53:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,who doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.36,0:53:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,spend energy. He doesn't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.89,0:53:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,spend. You're okay. He said, it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.35,0:53:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't a question. I nodded. He
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.80,0:53:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,came closer. Took my hand. It
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.72,0:53:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,was a quick gesture without the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.78,0:53:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,atrics. And I let him because my
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.89,0:53:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,hand
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.16,0:53:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,needed to be held. And I wasn't
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.03,0:53:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,going to pretend otherwise. The
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.91,0:53:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,police have arrived. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.18,0:53:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to go down. And you? He
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.04,0:53:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't answer right away. His
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.72,0:53:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,eyes traveled over my face like
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.51,0:53:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.92,0:53:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,checking whether a piece was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.49,0:53:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,missing, like someone taking a
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.18,0:53:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,silent inventory. I can't go
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.75,0:53:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,down with
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.26,0:53:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you. The police came in through
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.51,0:53:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the loading ramp. Exactly as
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.53,0:53:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Marcello had warned. Two of the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.78,0:53:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the three who had gone up the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.76,0:53:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,wrong stairs was collected
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.54,0:53:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,unconscious on the mezzanine
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.45,0:53:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.52,0:53:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No one asked why his wrist was
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.07,0:53:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,broken. Marcello said it had
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.51,0:53:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,happened during the flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.42,0:53:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I confirmed with a nod. Dario
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.08,0:53:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from the corner said nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.73,0:53:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever and didn't appear in the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.39,0:53:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.64,0:53:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he was somewhere in the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.12,0:53:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel. Probably in the top suite
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.69,0:54:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd reserved under the name of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.22,0:54:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,some company no one would verify
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.92,0:54:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that night. And I deliberately
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.52,0:54:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't tell the officers there
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.12,0:54:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,had been a fourth man on the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.06,0:54:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,ground floor. Marcello didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.08,0:54:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,say either. Neither did Dario.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.98,0:54:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first collective lie
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.37,0:54:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that hotel produced since I'd
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.68,0:54:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,been managing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.82,0:54:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know if it was
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.12,0:54:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion. I didn't know if it
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.87,0:54:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,was complicity. I only knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.67,0:54:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.08,0:54:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,lying seemed less wrong than
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.47,0:54:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,handing over someone who had
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.86,0:54:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed when he could have fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.78,0:54:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin was asked to leave by his
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.67,0:54:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,own sponsors. Rubino Tiano, who
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.49,0:54:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,had cut him off at the table
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.15,0:54:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,hours
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.44,0:54:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,before, made a point of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.89,0:54:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,accompanying him to the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.73,0:54:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of kindness, but to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.43,0:54:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ensure he left
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.32,0:54:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,without making a scene. Tisha
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.04,0:54:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,stayed. I saw when she
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.35,0:54:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,approached one of the hotel's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.07,0:54:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,press office
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.78,0:54:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,journalists and said three
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.12,0:54:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sentences I couldn't hear. The
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.66,0:54:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,journalist nodded and took
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.99,0:54:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.82,0:54:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,At one in the morning, the hall
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.31,0:54:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,was empty. The chairs had been
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.76,0:54:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,stacked by the waiters without
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.20,0:54:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone asking. The sound system
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.17,0:54:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,was off, the overhead lights
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.96,0:54:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,out. Only the low wall lights
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.81,0:55:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,gave
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.06,0:55:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the room that yellowish end of
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.63,0:55:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,night tone. And the feeling was
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.26,0:55:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that of a theater after the last
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.94,0:55:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,showing. That quiet that isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.76,0:55:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,peace, but what's left after
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.46,0:55:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.42,0:55:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I went up to the fourth floor
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.81,0:55:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,balcony by the stairs I now knew
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.34,0:55:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in all their curves.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.80,0:55:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The balcony looked out over the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.50,0:55:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,avenue, and the avenue looked
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.09,0:55:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,out over the lake. And the lake,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.32,0:55:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,at that hour, was just a black
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.19,0:55:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,stripe, with lights blinking on
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.13,0:55:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the horizon like punctuation
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.88,0:55:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,without a sentence. The air had
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.74,0:55:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that specific smell of Chicago
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.54,0:55:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.48,0:55:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Concrete, north wind, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.37,0:55:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,damp promise of a rain that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.13,0:55:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't coming. I rested my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.22,0:55:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,on the stone parapet. The
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.75,0:55:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,surface was cold and slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.52,0:55:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,rough under my palms, and that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.35,0:55:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,simple
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.72,0:55:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,detail brought me more into the
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.23,0:55:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,present than anything else that
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.74,0:55:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,night. I knew he would find me
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.21,0:55:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.88,0:55:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I knew. I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.52,0:55:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the footsteps behind me before I
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.16,0:55:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,turned around.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.88,0:55:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,May I? He asked, standing about
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.42,0:55:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,three meters away. You may. He
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.88,0:55:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,came closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.50,0:56:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rested his hands on the parapet
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.00,0:56:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,beside me without touching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.46,0:56:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed like that for maybe a
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.96,0:56:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,whole minute, saying nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.66,0:56:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at the lights of the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.29,0:56:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,lake. It was the first time all
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.11,0:56:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,night
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.40,0:56:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that the silence between us had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.20,0:56:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,no calculation. It was just
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.78,0:56:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,silence, and it had a different
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.58,0:56:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,weight than I expected. I owe
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.79,0:56:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you the truth. He said, finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.23,0:56:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you owe me more than that. I
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.36,0:56:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,know.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.74,0:56:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I waited. He started from the
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.50,0:56:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,beginning. He said he'd entered
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.38,0:56:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the app's ad because a source
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.14,0:56:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,had
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.32,0:56:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,indicated that someone inside
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.68,0:56:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the hotel was laundering money
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.09,0:56:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,through the season's events,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.82,0:56:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and that that night's charity
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.24,0:56:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,gala was the turning point of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.66,0:56:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the accounts. He said he'd
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.93,0:56:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.22,0:56:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,my request because Calvin's last
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.88,0:56:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,name was on the list of invited
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.49,0:56:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,sponsors, and Calvin was one of
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.10,0:56:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the suspects. He said he planned
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.95,0:56:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to observe the night, identify
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.68,0:56:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the operator, and leave before
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.42,0:56:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,midnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.94,0:56:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you showed up. He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.02,0:56:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you did everything wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.84,0:56:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,from my point of view. You
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.53,0:56:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.92,0:56:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,need me. You used me as an
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.53,0:56:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,accessory and did the job
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.07,0:56:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself. I used you as an
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.68,0:56:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,accessory all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.44,0:56:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It was the first time in
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.91,0:57:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,many years that someone looked
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.29,0:57:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,at me thinking I was just
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.43,0:57:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,decoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.60,0:57:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.00,0:57:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that. I looked at him. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.40,0:57:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the first time that night I was
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.90,0:57:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,looking at him without deciding
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.46,0:57:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what to feel before looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.87,0:57:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the head of the Malvani
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.39,0:57:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,family.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.74,0:57:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I am. You've had people
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.71,0:57:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,killed. Some. I won't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.57,0:57:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You were
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.34,0:57:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,going to use me. I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.92,0:57:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And now he took something from
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.78,0:57:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner pocket of the Tuxedo.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.71,0:57:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a black flash drive with
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.64,0:57:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.76,0:57:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,identification. Nothing that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.77,0:57:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,said what it held. Here. He
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.70,0:57:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,said, and held it out to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.71,0:57:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.04,0:57:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The evidence on Calvin. Yes. The
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.33,0:57:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,accounts, the destinations, the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.55,0:57:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,dates, and there's something
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.56,0:57:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,else too.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.20,0:57:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that connects this
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.05,0:57:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,night to me. If you hand this
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.90,0:57:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,over, Calvin goes to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.22,0:57:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And so do I. I looked at the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.02,0:57:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,flash drive in his palm. I
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.70,0:57:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't take it. Why are you
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.43,0:57:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,giving me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.70,0:57:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I promised myself in the
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.45,0:57:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,service hallway that I would no
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.15,0:57:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,longer manipulate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.58,0:58:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't keep that promise
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.28,0:58:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,holding onto this. I stayed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.86,0:58:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,silent for a moment. You knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.92,0:58:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you walked into the hall, I
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.98,0:58:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,said slowly that you were going
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.97,0:58:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to care? No. When did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.96,0:58:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hallway. When you laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.63,0:58:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,before you cried. It was the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.10,0:58:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,most honest sentence anyone had
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.72,0:58:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,said to me in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.40,0:58:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,years. It had no explanation, no
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.41,0:58:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,qualification. Nothing beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.23,0:58:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the sentence itself existing in
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.18,0:58:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the space between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.74,0:58:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I took the flash drive. I closed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.63,0:58:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,my hand over it. I put it in the
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.52,0:58:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,pocket of my dress. I haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.23,0:58:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiven you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.20,0:58:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I know. But I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.33,0:58:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,keep this. You can keep it. You
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.60,0:58:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,turn to face me. His hand rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.88,0:58:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly. And hung in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.53,0:58:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,between us for two seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.11,0:58:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,before it touched my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.10,0:58:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a touch that asked
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.47,0:58:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,permission without asking a
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.94,0:58:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,question. The warm palm against
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.64,0:58:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,my face
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.02,0:58:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,cold from the night. I kissed
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.23,0:58:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,him first, not on impulse. By
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.44,0:58:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,choice. The kiss was slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.92,0:58:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,without hunger, without victory
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.75,0:58:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,on either side. It was a kiss of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.63,0:58:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who had survived a
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.16,0:59:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,night that should have ended a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.71,0:59:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,different way. And had decided
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.26,0:59:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,this way worked too. When we
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.71,0:59:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.02,0:59:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,apart, he rested his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.98,0:59:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,against mine. I felt his breath
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.07,0:59:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,steadying. Like mine. Do you
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.96,0:59:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,want to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.58,0:59:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He asked. It wasn't a question
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.38,0:59:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about the balcony. It was a
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.00,0:59:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,question about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.50,0:59:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I do. He took my hand. We walked
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.10,0:59:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,down the sweet hallway in
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.12,0:59:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,silence, and the carpet muffled
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.64,0:59:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,our
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.88,0:59:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,footsteps the same way it had
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.53,0:59:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,muffled his. When I still
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.96,0:59:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,thought I knew who he was, the
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.67,0:59:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,sweet door
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.24,0:59:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,opened onto a room that smelled
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.15,0:59:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of new wood, and something woody
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.11,0:59:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't name. Amber, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.46,0:59:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Or simply the smell of a closed
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.25,0:59:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,place that had kept warmth. The
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.04,0:59:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,door closed behind us. I woke
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.72,0:59:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,before him. The light came in
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.31,0:59:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,through the half-open balcony
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.90,0:59:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,curtain in a thin golden strip,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.06,0:59:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,crossing the pale rug, and
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.40,0:59:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,stopping exactly at the foot of
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.00,0:59:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the bed, as if it had been
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.34,0:59:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,positioned
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.86,0:59:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with care. I lay there for maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.77,0:59:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,two minutes, just listening to
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.57,0:59:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his breathing beside me. It was
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.42,0:59:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a bomb breathing. Comer than I
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.98,1:00:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,expected from a man who'd seen
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.53,1:00:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,his own face on national
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.78,1:00:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,television
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.30,1:00:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about eight hours before. I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.02,1:00:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,turned slowly to look at him. He
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.07,1:00:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,was on his stomach. One arm over
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.11,1:00:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.30,1:00:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,pillow and the other fallen at
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.06,1:00:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,his side. Palm turned up. The
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.76,1:00:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,marks of the night were all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.35,1:00:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.00,1:00:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,without cosmetics. A fine cut on
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.06,1:00:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,his left forearm with the edge
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.98,1:00:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,already dry. A purplish
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.46,1:00:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mark on his right shoulder that
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.69,1:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,must have come from when he
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.77,1:00:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,disarmed the intruder on the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.88,1:00:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,landing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.20,1:00:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The skin, darkened in a wide
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.32,1:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,band I hadn't noticed at the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.44,1:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,time. His hair, which he
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.26,1:00:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,combed with almost irritating
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.95,1:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,precision, was fallen to one
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.57,1:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,side over his forehead. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.32,1:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the first
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.84,1:00:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,time I saw his face with nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.54,1:00:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in front of it. Without the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.97,1:00:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,calculation of the hall,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.62,1:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,without the silence of the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.12,1:00:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,backstage, without the flash
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.73,1:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,drive in his hand. I got out of
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.52,1:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,bed in silence,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.00,1:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,stepping slowly on the cold rug.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.52,1:00:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I put on the robe that was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.58,1:00:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,folded on the armchair. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.94,1:00:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.18,1:00:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,initials embroidered on the
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.57,1:00:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeve, and it was almost funny
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.17,1:00:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to think that I was in a room I
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.77,1:00:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,myself
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.08,1:00:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,had inventoryed three months
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.66,1:01:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,earlier, that I knew the model
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.35,1:01:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the bathtub, and the brand of
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.15,1:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.32,1:01:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,soap, and the kitchens internal
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.58,1:01:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,extension number. I walked out
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.77,1:01:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to the sweet balcony.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.40,1:01:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicago on a Sunday morning was
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.62,1:01:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,different. It had no hurry at
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.70,1:01:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all. The lake was silvery. Still
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.00,1:01:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with that early morning color
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.46,1:01:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that vanishes the moment the sun
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.07,1:01:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,rises fully, and the buildings
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.58,1:01:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,on the other side reflected a
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.33,1:01:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,cold, almost transparent light.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.19,1:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The air smelled of water and
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.88,1:01:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,damp asphalt. That specific
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.44,1:01:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,smell the city only has when the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.28,1:01:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,noise of the day hasn't yet
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.83,1:01:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,begun.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.70,1:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The breakfast car arrived in 15
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.36,1:01:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes. The sweet service had
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.96,1:01:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,known my name forever,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.56,1:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and so no one asked anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.95,1:01:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The young man who pushed the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.30,1:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,cart to the balcony just smiled,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.32,1:01:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,made a discreet bow, and left
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.98,1:01:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,without dragging the door. I sat
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.81,1:01:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of the two iron chairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.52,1:01:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I poured the coffee. I looked at
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.29,1:01:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the headline strip that had come
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.05,1:01:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,folded on top of the napkin,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.16,1:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,a hotel custom, leaving the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.74,1:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,front page with breakfast. A
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.38,1:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,habit I myself had approved when
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.26,1:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I re-negotiated
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.14,1:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the executive floor contract.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.93,1:02:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Calvin was the headline.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.41,1:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Investigation opened into
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.95,1:02:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,diversion in the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.94,1:02:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,2022 campaign. A profile photo
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.12,1:02:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of him. Bad. With his eyes half
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.37,1:02:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,closed and his chin raised the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.54,1:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,way
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.76,1:02:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he did when he thought he was
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.13,1:02:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the most important person in the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.64,1:02:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,room. I looked at it for two
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.96,1:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.34,1:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt nothing. No satisfaction
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.65,1:02:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with a sharp tooth, no residual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.96,1:02:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,pain, no need to reread the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.97,1:02:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.20,1:02:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the quiet recognition that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.81,1:02:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it was exactly what needed to
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.31,1:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,happen. It was the first relief
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.92,1:02:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.02,1:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the morning. You woke up early.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.87,1:02:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up. I've ran with
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.43,1:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,standing in the balcony doorway,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.96,1:02:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,barefoot on the cold floor of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.50,1:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the terrace, wearing the tuxedo
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.14,1:02:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pants and a white shirt open at
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.78,1:02:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.94,1:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,top three buttons. He'd washed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.71,1:02:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,his face. His eyes were clear
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.42,1:02:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the way eyes get after very
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.01,1:02:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,little
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.92,1:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you sleep too late. I answered.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.83,1:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He laughed. It was the first
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.55,1:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,time I heard him really laughed
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.46,1:02:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and the laugh was short, low of
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.47,1:02:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who didn't have the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.21,1:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,habit but also wasn't
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.57,1:02:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,apologizing for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.02,1:02:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He sat in the other chair,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.57,1:03:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,poured his own coffee. He said
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.37,1:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing for a moment and the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.04,1:03:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,silence
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.46,1:03:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,between us didn't have the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.83,1:03:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,weight of needing to be filled.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.46,1:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I need to give
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.14,1:03:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you. He said.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.20,1:03:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He took a flash drive from his
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.63,1:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,pants pocket. It was identical
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.06,1:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to the one on the balcony the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.44,1:03:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,night before.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.06,1:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Same size, same matte metal
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.07,1:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,color. For half a second, I
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.09,1:03:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thought it was the same one
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.10,1:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'd kept it and was going
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.76,1:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to take back what he'd handed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.30,1:03:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,over. This one is the complete
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.91,1:03:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.28,1:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He said. The one from last night
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.01,1:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,only had Calvin and the part
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.53,1:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that publicly connects me to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.04,1:03:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,this
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.26,1:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,night. This one has everything
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.21,1:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,else. The names that haven't
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.03,1:03:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,been said yet, the dates, the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.91,1:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,accounts,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.24,1:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,including what could protect me
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.48,1:03:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,if I needed. The two together
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.58,1:03:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,tell the whole story. I want you
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.90,1:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.04,1:03:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,look at the flash drive on the
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.87,1:03:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,table between my cup and his.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.65,1:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The metal reflected a point of
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.48,1:03:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,light from the sky. Why me?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.13,1:03:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the only person I trust
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.03,1:03:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to make that choice isn't me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.18,1:03:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I took a sip of coffee. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.97,1:03:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,good. Full bodyed with a bitter
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.81,1:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,undertone the sweet service
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.42,1:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,always got right. The lake down
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.26,1:04:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,below had begun to gain color.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.04,1:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.02,1:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said after a short silence,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.01,1:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but not today. Today I just want
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.20,1:04:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to have coffee. He nodded. His
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.26,1:04:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,phone
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.60,1:04:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,rang on the table. He looked. He
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.96,1:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't answer. Sir I, I said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.03,1:04:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,before he could ask,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.92,1:04:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just texted her now. She'll
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.52,1:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,call me in three minutes if I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.12,1:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,don't answer in person. My phone
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.88,1:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,rang. Two minutes. I corrected.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.16,1:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I answered. Are you alive? Sir I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.51,1:04:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,said without a greeting,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.94,1:04:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,without a good morning, without
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.01,1:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,anything. I am in one piece, in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.08,1:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,one piece, which floor of the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.02,1:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hotel.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.42,1:04:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not answering that. Noelia
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.55,1:04:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cross, you're in the suite of
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.60,1:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what. I'm having coffee. I hate
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.80,1:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.30,1:04:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you. I'm going to kill
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.25,1:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you. I'm going to buy you a
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.06,1:04:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,dress in what order. I laughed.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.15,1:04:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.82,1:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,first time in the whole night in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.13,1:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole morning that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.35,1:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,without holding anything back.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.04,1:04:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll decide the order later. I
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.86,1:04:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,said. I'll call you this
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.27,1:05:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,afternoon. Are you with him? I
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.03,1:05:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.56,1:05:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone. He was looking at the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.14,1:05:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lake as if the conversation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.52,1:05:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,warned about him. His fingers
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.00,1:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,wrapped
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.36,1:05:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,up. I am. Everything okay there?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.69,1:05:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's okay here. I hung
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.88,1:05:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,up. There was a knock on the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.92,1:05:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,suite door. Three identical
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.99,1:05:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,knocks spaced out. Dario,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.90,1:05:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone said without moving. I
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.27,1:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,got up and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.04,1:05:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,went to open it. Dario was in
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.43,1:05:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the hallway wearing the same
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.77,1:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,dark suit from the night before,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.72,1:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but the tie had disappeared at
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.30,1:05:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,some point, and the top button
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.88,1:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of his shirt was undone. He
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.30,1:05:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,looked
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.62,1:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,at me with the expression of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.91,1:05:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who had seen too many
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.24,1:05:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,things in the last few hours,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.58,1:05:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but had no intention of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.97,1:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,commenting on any of them. Give
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.85,1:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,a minimal nod and looked over my
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.78,1:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,shoulder into the suite. The car
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.27,1:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is downstairs. He said, did you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.68,1:05:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sleep? I asked. I blinked.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.04,1:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that count as sleeping? In
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.25,1:05:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,some cultures? Yes. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.10,1:05:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,almost a smile. Almost. I went
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.24,1:05:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,back to the
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.02,1:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,balcony. Everyone was standing,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.89,1:05:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,putting on the Tuxedo jacket,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.65,1:05:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,carefully folding the left
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.22,1:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeve to
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.76,1:05:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,cover the cut. I need to ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.80,1:06:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,something before you go down. I
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.78,1:06:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,said, ask. What exactly are you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.76,1:06:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,asking me for? He stopped
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.34,1:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,folding the sleeve. A chance. He
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.36,1:06:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,said, I'm not promising I'll
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.13,1:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,stop being
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.76,1:06:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,dangerous. I'm not promising
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.24,1:06:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,marriage or a change of address
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.88,1:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,or anything on paper. I'm
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.20,1:06:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,promising
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.68,1:06:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,not to lie to you. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.18,1:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm asking you to let me be
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.74,1:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,close while I dismantle what can
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.34,1:06:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,be dismantled. And what can't
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.35,1:06:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,be? We'll see. It was little. It
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.58,1:06:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,was also the most honest
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.24,1:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sentence
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.80,1:06:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a man like him could construct.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.63,1:06:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew the difference
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.11,1:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,between an empty promise and a
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.89,1:06:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,promise
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.30,1:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,small enough to be real. All
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.41,1:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,right. I said, he came closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.66,1:06:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Took my hand. He pressed his
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.77,1:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lips to my
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.52,1:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,palm once, without the atrics,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.69,1:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,without haste, and let me go. We
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.00,1:06:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,went down together. Dario in
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.03,1:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,front,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.90,1:06:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the two of us behind. The
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.52,1:06:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,hallway long and silent at that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.53,1:06:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hour. In the lobby, Calvin's
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.34,1:06:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,headline
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.86,1:06:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,was on the new stand in the
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.35,1:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,corner. Under a cold ceiling
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.89,1:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,light, I looked at it for two
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.49,1:06:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,seconds
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.88,1:06:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and kept walking. Evern's car
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.56,1:07:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,was parked at the side entrance
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.36,1:07:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,where the photographers had no
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.10,1:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,access authorization. He turned
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.47,1:07:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to me before getting in. I'll
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.68,1:07:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,call you today. Okay. Noelia.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.89,1:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.70,1:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I didn't ask what
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.55,1:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,for. I thought I knew. He got
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.46,1:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,into the car. The door closed
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.37,1:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with that
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.96,1:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,sound of an armored car. Heavy
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.70,1:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and definitive. I saw through
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.38,1:07:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the dark window that he settled
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.18,1:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,into the back seat and that for
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.10,1:07:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,half a second before the car
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.83,1:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled away. He looked at me
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.57,1:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,through
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.00,1:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the glass. I didn't see the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.42,1:07:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,other person who was in the back
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.11,1:07:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,seat. Evern's car didn't leave
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.70,1:07:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.96,1:07:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,away. I saw through the dark
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.75,1:07:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,window of the back seat. The
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.54,1:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,silhouette of a second person
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.40,1:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,beside him.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.38,1:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone with gray hair, I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.01,1:07:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize. Someone who reached
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.53,1:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,out and touched his arm with a
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.06,1:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,comb that seemed old. I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.16,1:07:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,hear what they said. I only saw
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.34,1:07:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Evern nod once, slowly, and the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.51,1:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,car
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.72,1:07:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,pulled onto the avenue. I took a
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.73,1:07:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,taxi home. I didn't want the
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.48,1:07:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,hotels car. I wanted the time
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.30,1:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,between
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.74,1:07:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the hotel and my apartment, and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.43,1:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the taxi gave me exactly 20
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.91,1:08:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes with the window cracked
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.60,1:08:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.98,1:08:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,cold smell of Sunday coming in.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.78,1:08:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My apartment door opened with
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.46,1:08:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the same sound as always. That
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.20,1:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,light creek of the hinge I
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.69,1:08:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,always promised to fix. Things
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.41,1:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,were where I'd left them. The
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.08,1:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,shoebox
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.48,1:08:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in the hallway. The previous
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.09,1:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,day's cup in the sink. The coat
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.86,1:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,on the back of the chair. It was
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.70,1:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,strange
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.10,1:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,how nothing there had changed,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.87,1:08:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and how inside me everything
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.53,1:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,seemed to have shifted places
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.25,1:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.66,1:08:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,asking permission. I closed the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.62,1:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,door. I leaned my back against
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.52,1:08:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it. I let out my breath slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.14,1:08:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was okay. Everything
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.79,1:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,was at peace. I brought my hand
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.45,1:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to the road pocket,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.00,1:08:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and felt the flash drive between
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.66,1:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,my fingers. And only then
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.96,1:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,remembered I'd brought the hotel
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.62,1:08:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,robe without noticing. With the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.36,1:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,initials embroidered on the
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.88,1:08:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,sleeve and all, it was strange
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.57,1:08:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to know
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.96,1:08:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so little about the past of
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.62,1:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,someone I had just chosen to
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.08,1:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the greatest danger of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.12,1:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,my life had been hiring ever and
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.16,1:09:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for one night. But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.28,1:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The real danger began when I
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.05,1:09:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,started to believe that, by his
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.00,1:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,side, I could finally be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.20,1:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He loved me without hiding it,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.10,1:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,protected me without confining
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.99,1:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.26,1:09:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms around me felt like the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.05,1:09:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,only safe place in the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.90,1:09:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,until I found the envelope
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.53,1:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,hidden in his drawer. Three
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.22,1:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,photos.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.84,1:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My face marked on the screen of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.40,1:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a news report that hadn't yet
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.86,1:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,aired.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.26,1:09:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A transfer receipt with the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.86,1:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,exact date of the worst night of
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.75,1:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my life, and a message from him,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.00,1:09:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,short, sent to a number I didn't
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.83,1:09:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,recognize. She can't find out.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.12,1:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Within a few hours, my life
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.12,1:09:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,became a headline. The same
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.11,1:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,people who applauded me now,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.42,1:09:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,looked at me like an accomplice,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.41,1:09:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,doors slammed in my face. Voices
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.39,1:09:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,accused me terribly of something
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.38,1:09:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even understand. An
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.37,1:09:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,evern, the man who swore to
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,protect me, disappeared for
